WEBVTT

00:04:26.114 --> 00:04:30.148
ambapo watu wameanza kusema,
"Tunajukumu."

00:04:30.262 --> 00:04:33.125
Hivyo ninapoongea na hawa viongozi, nasema,

00:04:33.149 --> 00:04:37.095
"Ona, unaweza kua mkurugenzi mtendaji,
mwenye mafanikio sana kwenye kampuni,

00:04:37.105 --> 00:04:39.628
lakini unaweza pia kua karani."

00:04:39.662 --> 00:04:41.013
Na hilo ni neno la msingi.

00:04:41.027 --> 00:04:44.100
"Unaweza kua karani
wa mamlaka uliyonayo

00:04:44.100 --> 00:04:48.642
kuunda maisha na uchumi
wa mabilioni ya watu.

00:04:48.689 --> 00:04:50.631
Ni ipi unataka kua?"

00:04:51.201 --> 00:04:54.645
Na jibu ni,
sio moja wala lingine.

00:04:54.689 --> 00:04:56.792
Hiki ndicho tunachokosa sasa hivi.

00:04:56.802 --> 00:05:01.203
Hivyo pale mtu mzima kama Brad Smith,
raisi wa Microsoft,